答番你啲問題<br />
<br />
1. 如果你個method係想用嚟print野落stdout 咁的確return係多餘<br />
- 1. 改return type由int做void<br />
- 2. 刪咗行return statement<br />
<pre><code data-type="java">public class Main {
 public static void hello(int a, int b) {
  System.out.println(&quot;hello world&quot; + a + b);
 }
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
2. 你可以用method做一舉兩得嘅功能 但係唔建議<br />
- 參考下SOLID principle嘅single responsibility principle<br />
- 簡單嚟講method只應該做佢應該做嘅野<br />
<br />
3. 你留心睇下 你個block係有2個statements<br />
- 你行完System.out.println<br />
- 仲有個return statement<br />
- 當method個block入面所有statements都行晒<br />
- 又或者遇到return/throw (不考慮try加埋finally)<br />
- 成個method先會完結<br />
- 比個例子你:<br />
<pre><code data-type="java">public class Main {
 public static boolean isZero(int value) {
  if (value == 0) {
   return false;
   // after executing return statement, method will be terminated
  }

  System.out.print(&quot;value does not equal to 0.&quot;);

  return true;
  // after executing return statement, method will be terminated
 }
}</code></pre><br />
- 1. 當value == 0<br />
- 2. reach到return false個return statement<br />
- 3. 成個method就會完 下面嘅code唔會再行<br />
<br />
- 1. 否則value != 0<br />
- 2. 就會唔入上面個if block<br />
- 3. 直接行System.out.println<br />
- 4. 再行return true個return statement<br />
- 5. 之後個method先算完

