因為一開始無initialize variable<br />
<br />
上面位巴打可能寫開其他lang<br />
java 係pass by value<br />
<br />
JAVA<br />
<pre><code data-type="">public static void main(String[] args){
    int answer = calculate(1,1);
    System.out.println(answer);
}

private static void calculate(int a, int b){
    return a + b;
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
如果用C++寫就可以寫到咁 (無記錯syntax既話）<br />
<pre><code data-type="">int main(){
    int answer;
    calculate(1,1,answer);
    cout &lt;&lt; answer;
    return 0;
}

int calculate(int a, int b, int&amp; c){
    c = a + b;
}</code></pre>

首先理解咗function 嘅用法係比你可以拆件嚟處理複雜嘅問題或者程序上可以分開唔同parts等佢可以獨立處理一個問題<br />
要具體解釋用一個比較簡單嘅問題去模擬情影會比較好理解<br />
例如上面有講過嘅factorial係一個好例子, 如果我今日要user input一個數字我再計返個factorial, 咁function嘅意義除左可以幫我分開處理user input之外, function 嘅return statement仲可以幫我簡化個calculation去提升效率<br />
例如<br />
<pre><code data-type="">import java.util.Scanner;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);     
        System.out.print(&quot;Enter an integer: &quot;);
        int number = input.nextInt();
        System.out.println(&quot;You entered &quot; + number);
        // closing the scanner object
        input.close();
    }
}</code></pre><br />
我地要另外處理user input等佢唔比人入其他垃圾之後又可以拎返個input 嚟用, 可以變成一個function, 下面就係唔比user入一個負數同個數一定要細過100<br />
<pre><code data-type="">import java.util.Scanner;

class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int i = Main.handleUserInput();
    }

    public static int handleUserInput() {
        Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.print(&quot;Enter an integer below 100: &quot;);
        int number = input.nextInt();
        System.out.println(&quot;You entered &quot; + number);
        input.close();
        if(number &gt;= 100 or number &lt;= 0){
            return 0;
        }
        else{
            return number;
        }
    }
}</code></pre><br />
之後如果要再處理factorial 就會變成咁<br />
<pre><code data-type="">import java.util.Scanner;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int i = Main.handleUserInput();
        int f = Main.factorial(i);
        System.out.println(f);
    }

    public static int handleUserInput() {
        Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);

        System.out.print(&quot;Enter an integer below 100: &quot;);
        int number = input.nextInt();
        System.out.println(&quot;You entered &quot; + number);
        input.close();
        if(number &gt;= 100 || number &lt;= 0){
            return 0;
        }
        else{
            return number;
        }
    }

    public static int factorial(int number){
        int result = 1;
        if(number &lt;= 1){
            result = 1;
        }else{
            for(int j = 1;j =&lt; number;j++){
                result = result * j;
            }
        }
        return result;
    }
}
 ```
最後既然知道factorial係由1乘到去俾出嚟嗰個數, 咁其實可以唔用loop做,因為覺得用loop好傻仔 (喺其他問題上面或者有效率提升, 但factorial冇乜)
咁就要用function return返上一個數嘅答案畀個function自己等佢可以繼續計落去, 變成咁</code></pre><br />
import java.util.Scanner;<br />
<br />
class Main {<br />
    public static void main(String[] args) {<br />
        int i = Main.handleUserInput();<br />
        int f = Main.factorial(i);<br />
        System.out.println(f);<br />
    }<br />
    <br />
    public static int handleUserInput() {<br />
        Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);<br />
        System.out.print(&quot;Enter an integer below 100: &quot;);<br />
        int number = input.nextInt();<br />
        System.out.println(&quot;You entered &quot; + number);<br />
        input.close();<br />
        if(number &gt;= 100 || number &lt;= 0){<br />
            return 0;<br />
        }<br />
        else{<br />
